{"tid":2264424,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩去左家族飯局 00後表妹問電視機個肥婆係邊個？","createTime":"2020-10-30T15:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T20:58:22.000Z","uid":42246,"like":14,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"29c33e496058e6d0bb536ecac7d91a7ece82c87c","tid":2264424,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"親戚見可以6個人食飯 <br />\n就約左我一家去酒樓食個晚飯<br />\n咁間垃圾酒樓就播tvb<br />\n突然間00後表妹同大家講<br />\n「嘩乜依家d 廣告拍攝成本咁低 用部低清cam搵個肥婆拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁我就望一望啦 <br />\n頂你個肺 肥姐來既<br />\n有生之年竟然重睇到肥姐賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntvb 2020死人都拎出來消費<br />\n（金象米廣告）<br />\n<br />\n跟著我就笑我表妹 <br />\n<span class=\"red\">全香港娛樂圈最大黑澀會美眉你都唔識？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後表妹 面都紅埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n谷著谷著咁<br />\n我再講多句「哎 依家d 00真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知佢一句彈埋來<br />\n「係唔識架啦，依d死老野係得死老野先識。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突然間 我即刻灰左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢講得岩 90後真係變左死老野了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正評：我代表90後肉體上懲罰00後表妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />負評：90後死老野收皮啦 返去老人屋到老死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347b42b61bf457eb877d33fbac09a9dc1ce3c09c","tid":2264424,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:30:25.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"6329b212d1ca1660777050681d017783eb644425","tid":2264424,"uid":374184,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e152e63cacad84c4eaa193d51149d3e1ff367089","tid":2264424,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"樓主真心柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5eb8d6471a4dbc4f36d1a4ddc0c25142fcdb0f0","tid":2264424,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e152e63cacad84c4eaa193d51149d3e1ff367089","tid":2264424,"uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"樓主真心柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"真係暴露左年齡<br />\n<br />\n我以為大家重知肥姐係邊個<br />\n<br />\n點知原來肥姐08年就死左 佢個陣先得幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家佢大到識叫我死老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p